#: ../../source/preferences/manage-your-security-preferences.rst:7
msgid ""
"Select your profile picture, select **Profile**, and then select "
"**Security** to configure your password, view access history, and to view"
" or logout of active sessions."
msgstr "프로필 사진을 선택하고 **프로필** 을 선택한 다음 **보안** 을 선택하여 비밀번호를 구성하고, 접근 기록을 확인하며, 활성 세션을 확인하거나 로그아웃할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../source/preferences/manage-your-security-preferences.rst:10
msgid "**Security setting**"
msgstr "**보안 설정**"

#: ../../source/preferences/manage-your-security-preferences.rst:10
